===Land Forces Command=== {{main|Kommando Landstreitkräfte}}
The Land Forces Command ({{lang-de|Kommando Landstreitkräfte}}) was established on 1 December 1972 as a management body created for the land forces. The seat was in [[Wildpark-West]]. The [[Friedrich Engels Guard Regiment]] provide security and guard services for the Land Forces Command headquarters.
