* Oberst [[Erwin Freyer]], 1 March 1956 to 1 May 1957 * Generalmajor [[Rudolf Menzel]], 1 May 1957 to 14 October 1959 * Generalmajor [[Friedrich Dickel]], 15 October 1959 to 14 November 1963 * Generalmajor [[Werner Fleißner]], 1 February 1964 to 27 December 1985 * Generaloberst [[Joachim Goldbach]], 1 February 1986 to 18 April 1990
